{"by":"dchuk","id":47773103,"kids":[47774390,47773360],"parent":47768750,"text":"Ignore all the hate in the comments here, anyone denying the direction of software development and it aggressively becoming agentic have their own reckonings to deal with…<p>I love this concept. While I’m a Rails guy myself, I appreciate the value of Django too, and an agent-optimized version of it makes sense.<p>I feel like the next logical steps are this exact concept but in Go &#x2F; Rust to get even more performance out of everything and to also get the single deployable binary too","time":1776211787,"type":"comment"}